articles.author: Jack Guy
articles.title: 102 snakes removed from homeowner’s garden in Sydney - CNN
articles.description: Living in Australia means you might have to accept coming across a snake or two on your property at some point. But one Sydney homeowner got more than he bargained for when a snake catcher unearthed 102 of the slithery reptiles hiding in his garden.
